<%= javascript_import_module_tag "application" %>
<section class="section home-section">
    <h1>Home</h1>
    <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <article class="home-img-container bg-color-one">
                <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2021/04/27/16/12/succulents-6211878_1280.png" class="home-plant-img" alt="succulent plant pots "/>
                <div class="home-img-text-container">
                    <p>Hey, great, you are signed in!</p>
                    <p>Enjoy using this site, and I hope it is helpful.</p>
                </div>
        </article>
    <% else%>
        <article class="home-img-container bg-color-two">
            <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2021/04/27/16/12/succulents-6211878_1280.png" class="home-plant-img" alt="succulent plant pots "/>
            <div class="home-img-text-container">
                <p>Hello, great to see you here!</p> 
                <p>You are visiting this site as a guest.</p>
                <p>create an account to get the most out of this tool, save your progress and see your pot grow!</p>
            </div>
        </article>
    <% end%>
    <article class="home-intro-para">
        <p>This is a tool designed to help people get into saving on a regular basis.</p>
        <p>The idea is that you give yourself a monthly target, and then you log your actual savings
            every month. The website will save your progress and is a convenient way to keep 
            track. 
        </p>
    </article>
</section>

